data.description: NEWLY REMODELED 5 BED 3 BATH HOME WITH A FABULOUS HEATED POOL AT A GREAT PRICE!  If you need space and style look no further. Home sits on a prime, OVERSIZED tree lined lot with tons of space to play, entertain or garden. Take in the soaring ceilings as you enter this freshly painted space. Luxurious granite counters and marble backsplash adorn this gourmet kitchen. Stainless appliances, gas range, large island and pantry. Owners suite and guest room are on main level and very private. Enjoy the soaking tub, double vanities and separate shower. Stylish wood look tile on entire main level and brand new carpet upstairs makes this home an obvious choice. New modern baseboards and plumbing fixtures are a plus. Everyone will delight in their own space with room to breathe. Extras include built in storage spaces, decking in attic, and stained concrete pool deck.  Bring the family and take a private tour of this move in ready home today ! Brand new elementary school is going in as well! Great time to make the move !
